{"tid":181560,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（2017年4月上旬）旬初天氣較涼；旬後期，海洋氣流帶來潮濕和暖天氣","createTime":"2017-03-31T16:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T19:29:31.000Z","uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de3026db3765c63d362a9fbcb4351896a07cbe28","tid":181560,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:53:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk017&h=0677eeb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">氣象討論：2017年4月上旬</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2017年4月1日至10日</span></strong></span><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><ins>◤溫度術語</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒 　　　　　≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷 　 　　　8 - 12 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">清涼　　　　13 - 17 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和暖／稍涼　18 - 22 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫暖　　　　23 - 27 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">炎熱　　　　28 - 32 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">酷熱 　　 　　≧ 33 &deg;C</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a98f4398\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ea4ece7b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftextonly%2Fexplain%2Fintroc.htm&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=187b558e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 短期氣候預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fseason%2Fseasonc.htm&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2b877c6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 香港天文台電腦預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fnhm%2Fnhm_uc.htm&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=ea674772\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8ef76d05\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/SuV1UB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FSuV1UB&h=aa5b9639&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/1mOf5kb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F1mOf5kb&h=f43ed746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 地面天氣圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a5ticH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a5ticH&h=b05f53f9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ahInaZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ahInaZ&h=2a1d8db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ajChbn&h=22f823b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ap2lTE&h=475ff2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a7TpCM&h=ef01e17d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2F1Oc5V&h=2e7774ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FMeu94L&h=e469b653&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FpSSahs&h=61ae872d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">氣象台專頁正式登場</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>我們自2008年起發表氣象帖。現在，一個屬於巴打絲打們的天氣專頁正式登場！我們以淺白易明的方式介紹氣象，讓您享受認識氣象箇中的樂趣。氣象不再沉悶空泛。<br />\n本專頁旨在為大家提供氣象相關的資訊，其中包括一些氣象小資料、即時的天氣及風暴等消息。設立的主要目的，是為了讓比較忙碌的巴打絲打們，即使沒時間或沒留意到高登氣象帖，都可透過另一個渠道獲得我們的氣象資訊。<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">請巴打絲打們到專頁讚好以示對我們支持及鼓勵</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=a112cb6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b52031f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/UTube\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FUTube&h=a22db7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tb%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1ad13165\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a></em></strong>"},{"pid":"8f824f9659f5cd19864b81de38aac1e7b73ddce6","tid":181560,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9464b021b5e9e31aa688e95e03d1770b90cde5","tid":181560,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T17:00:56.000Z","msg":"4月好舒服既第1日，希望熱天來之前，來緊仲有多次貨落來爽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efc763d66f1f148d5d7fe8d149edec83fa40a06","tid":181560,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T00:33:37.000Z","msg":"綠茶留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804c9b604445194a3de9377941cb731f4de950ae","tid":181560,"uid":79363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:01:19.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f6834c6fbc349154ac4f7585a64ff2a8c66b39","tid":181560,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T02:55:57.000Z","msg":"昨天成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nYesterday's Weather and Radiation Level<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Observatory:<br />\nMaximum Air Temperature: 23.7&deg;C<br />\nMinimum Air Temperature: 15.5&deg;C<br />\nGrass Minimum Temperature: 16.2&deg;C<br />\nRelative Humidity: 79 - 97%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Rainfall: 21.9 mm</span><br />\n<br />\nTotal rainfall since 1st January: 75.7 mm&nbsp;<br />\nAgainst an average of 161.3 mm&nbsp;"},{"pid":"dc7bd1cb8793d8b11bcb9865927869e5fe4d7b56","tid":181560,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"聽緊港台一台《大氣候》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2be9c7beece7ddcefe70c1f7b21717b96000bb","tid":181560,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"newpost lm"},{"pid":"6672080a54d6469cb748c4dc7819c1ba2375c48a","tid":181560,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"西太好似好靜一個風都冇"},{"pid":"c8c18c797a8011f44f11617ed9f6aa9596960feb","tid":181560,"uid":69680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>昨天成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nYesterday's Weather and Radiation Level<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Observatory:<br />\nMaximum Air Temperature: 23.7&deg;C<br />\nMinimum Air Temperature: 15.5&deg;C<br />\nGrass Minimum Temperature: 16.2&deg;C<br />\nRelative Humidity: 79 - 97%<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Rainfall: 21.9 mm</span><br />\n<br />\nTotal rainfall since 1st January: 75.7 mm&nbsp;<br />\nAgainst an average of 161.3 mm&nbsp;</blockquote><br />\nnice weather"},{"pid":"9dbfa2c95f4e7178a44baf232aeadd31cc54b0bf","tid":181560,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西太好似好靜一個風都冇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9706e814fc4adb488dde77d86fcba72547d63d","tid":181560,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T16:42:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i-w5cMcWA80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c